"{\"uid\": \"hngn.com-articles-260984-20240526-champs-elysees-paris-transform-massive-picnic-tablecloth-free-food-restaurants-olympics.htm\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"One of the world's most famous boulevards was the scene of a massive picnic Sunday as more than 4,000 people sat down on a 700-foot-long, red-and-white checkered \\\"tablecloth\\\" to feast on free food.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event on the Champs-Elys\\u00e9es in Paris, dubbed \\\"Le Grand Pique-Nique des Champs,\\\" drew applications from more than 270,000 people who hoped to take part, the French newspaperLe Mondereported.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039514818, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}, {\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.494495141759346e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 359, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9622827280804442, \"rank\": 0.037656442073743086, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the lucky winners, Yasmina Train of Paris, told theAssociated Pressthat picnicking on the City of Lights' iconic street between the Arc de Triomphe and Avenue Georges V was \\\"a dream coming true.\\\"\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.494495141759346e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.464563265389959e-13, \"text\": \"Arc de Triomphe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I took some pictures and I sent that to friends, you know, all over the world,\\\" Train said.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The meals, served in wicker picnic baskets, were prepared in eight \\\"temporary kitchens\\\" that were \\\"organized and managed by the grand chefs\\\" of eateries along the avenue, Marc-Antoine Jamet, chairperson of the Champs-Elys\\u00e9es Committee, told AP.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.999999999943384, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}, {\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andhra_Pradesh\", \"score\": 0.9414117750304887, \"rank\": 0.06198098246202887, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andhra_Pradesh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andhra_Pradesh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The offerings included creative sandwiches and puff pastries from restaurants that ranged from the famed Brasserie Foquet's to McDonald's,APsaid.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two sittings were scheduled at noon and 2 p.m. and the tablecloth was assembled on-site by 150 people from 25 pieces of recycled material, according to Le Monde.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Monde\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event, held exactly two months before Paris will host the opening ceremony of the Summer Olympcis, was aimed at boosting local interest in the Champs-Elys\\u00e9es, a popular tourist destination due to its designer boutiques and gourmet restaurants.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.494495141759346e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039514818, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it has fallen out of favor among Parisians, with the historic UGC Normandie movie theater, which opened in 1937, set to close next month following a decline in business, Le Monde reported.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/User-generated_content\", \"score\": 0.9999999999915872, \"rank\": 8.439300696671041e-12, \"text\": \"UGC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/User-generated_content\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/User-generated_content\"}, {\"begin\": 1567, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandie_Avenue\", \"score\": 0.9954885514740263, \"rank\": 0.004531794426678466, \"text\": \"Normandie\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandie_Avenue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandie_Avenue\"}, {\"begin\": 1671, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Monde\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Champs-Elys\\u00e9es Committee is scheduled to present an 1,800-page study with revitalization plans on Monday.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039514818, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 HNGN, All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not reproduce without permission.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": []}]}"